* The loop statement helps the programmer to execute a set of instruction repedatly :
    * Any looping statement has 3 parts :
                                          1) Initialization.
                                          2) Condition.
                                          3) Updations.

  1) Initialization : Specifiecs the starting point of a loop.
  2) Condition : Used to control the loop.
  3) Updation : It helps to reach the condition or make it false.
